{"tid":2149680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反送中至今近萬人被捕 控「暴動」最多 7月拘448人","createTime":"2020-08-10T13:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T14:03:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8561fc16a104d91824fc59d349f4353aa652a37","tid":2149680,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:50:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/4Z2HVHBOJXEIDXISKQRXVODAFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2F4Z2HVHBOJXEIDXISKQRXVODAFM%2F&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=7e848fee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2F4Z2HVHBOJXEIDXISKQRXVODAFM%2F&h=be5571d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/4Z2HVHBOJXEIDXISKQRXVODAFM/</a><br />\n<br />\n反修例運動至今近萬人被捕，惟檢控人數僅得約2成。警方今日（10日）在社交媒體上，公佈由去年6月9日至今年7月31日，涉及反修例運動中被捕及被控人數，當中有9,664人在運動中被捕，相比截至6月底的數字，僅一個月間再多448人被捕，最新檢控人數亦突破2千人大關(佔被捕人數約21%)。"},{"pid":"7a8c9da7d527ba6eaf9798566ff68368d71fd62e","tid":2149680,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9dcc51af00e519c92bd103155967dcc2b7149b6","tid":2149680,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:52:04.000Z","msg":"國際線有任 請每日推Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=b298eb81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"cdc5b4bced65f2c97f7b01ca50d4314a4ae1b627","tid":2149680,"uid":47356,"like":1,"disli